Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, \Nyour company is losing money.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Your company has a project. \NIt needs AI to get it done.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.00,0:00:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to send your data\Nto big AI like ChatGPT...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.00,0:00:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...but you can't. Your data is: \N Private. Confidential. Classified.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.00,0:00:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So companies strip the names off the data\Nand send it anyway.\NThey think it's safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not.\NThis is the first problem we solved.\N Stay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.00,0:00:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Eighty-seven percent of people \Ncan be re-identified from just \Na zip code, a gender, and a birth date. \NAnonymization is broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.50,0:00:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Your other details — age, location, diagnosis — \Nare enough to identify you. \NBig data connects the dots. \NBut we sidestep this problem completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.50,0:00:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We invented a new way \Nto combine all your office computers\N into one powerful AI.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.50,0:00:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Your data never leaves the building. \NSounds complicated? It's not. \NLet me show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.50,0:01:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad way number one: \NImagine five workers, but only one brain. \NOne puts it on, does his job. Takes it off, passes it to the next. \NEveryone else just stands there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.50,0:01:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's CrewAI, Swarms, LangGraph. \NAll their agents share one computer, one brain. \NOnly one thinks at a time. The rest wait. \N Doesn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.75,0:01:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad way number two: \NNow each worker has his own brain, \Nbut he works for a moment, stops, walks all the way \Nacross the room to hand off his piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.25,0:01:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...walks all the way back, works a little more. \NMost of the time — just walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.00,0:01:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Petals and Exo. They split one AI brain across computers. Each piece waits for the previous one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.25,0:01:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The slow network between them \Nkills everything. \NDoesn't work either.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The right way:\N Distributed parallel AI. \NNow imagine: before work begins, \Nevery worker gets the complete plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.50,0:02:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Every worker has his own brain. \NThe whistle blows, and they ALL start \Nworking at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.50,0:02:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody stops. \NNobody walks anywhere. \NNobody waits for anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.75,0:02:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Every computer gets its own complete AI \Nand its own piece of the project, \Nplanned in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.25,0:02:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They all think in parallel. \NThe project gets done \Nin a fraction of the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.25,0:02:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,With BeehiveOfAI, we got the full power of AI — \Nand not one patient record left this hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Our trade secrets \Nstayed inside our walls. \NNo leaks. No risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.75,0:02:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Every document stayed classified. \NFull AI capability. Zero exposure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.75,0:02:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Bob, you saved us a fortune. \NWe're running AI on our own computers now.\N I'm promoting you to Head of Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.25,0:02:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Bobby, you're the reason \Nour data stayed safe. \NI'm making you Senior Partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.00,0:02:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,For your service to this country... \NColonel Bob, \Nyour Hawaii vacation is approved.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.25,0:02:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Beehive of AI. \NNot another multi-agent framework. \NActual distributed parallel AI.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.25,0:03:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This technology can also \Nmake you money while you sleep — \Nwith your own computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.25,0:03:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Check out our Public Mode video. \Ngithub dot com slash strulovitz.
